main event: An unidentified flying object was sighted at Webb AFB, Texas on 14 Aug 61.
interesting points: The sighting lasted less than 1 minute,The object was described as elliptical, baseball-sized, and dull greyish metallic in color,The object emitted a blast of greenish-white exhaust,The observer was a USAF staff sergeant on duty at the base,Excellent weather conditions were noted at the time of the observation.
witness description: USAF SSGT Richard T. Dahlem, 3552th Civil Engineering Group
